    WHEN [dto.District].[ProvinceId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [dto.District.Province].[Id] AS [Id0], [dto.District.Province].[Code] AS [Code0], [dto.District.Province].[Name] AS [Name0], [dto.District.Province].[Rank] AS [Rank0], [dto.District.Province].[Status], [dto.District].[Status] AS [Status0], [dto].[Status] AS [Status1], [dto.District].[Id]
FROM [Ward] AS [dto]
INNER JOIN [District] AS [dto.District] ON [dto].[DistrictId] = [dto.District].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Province] AS [dto.District.Province] ON [dto.District].[ProvinceId] = [dto.District.Province].[Id]
